            "text": "Ephesians 4:25",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " and it becomes every man under the Gospel dispensation, according to the gift he has received, to speak, publish, and declare the truth of the Gospel, to the edification of others: ",
            "children": []
