        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "execute the judgment of truth and peace in your gates; that is, execute true judgment, as in Zechariah 7:9 do justice between man and man, without respect of persons; the issue of which will be peace between the contending parties: and this was to be done in their \"gates\", because there their courts of judicature were kept. ",
